INSTALL:
yum install tomcat wget -y

ENABLE AND START:
systemctl enable tomcat
systemctl start tomcat


/etc/tomcat
/var/log/tomcat
/var/log/tomcat 


LOCATION:
cd /usr/share/tomcat/

DOCUMENT ROOT:
cd /usr/share/tomcat/webapps/


CONFIG FILE
cd /usr/share/tomcat/conf/server.xml

systemctl restart tomcat

LOCATIONS MAY VARY BASED ON OS, CHECK STATUS OF SERVCIE TO GET THE FILE LOCATION
